EVENT "Programmation en E.5"
PICTURE obligement10:datas/FondTexte01
RESOLUTION 640 256 3 29000
TABS 100 200 300 400 500
MARGINS on 32 607
PALETTE 064040 0c4848 000 22d fb0 fff 7f2222 7f22dd
COLOR 4 2 11 0 0 14 4 0 0 4 4 6 2 2 4
